# Ignore everything at repo root by default
/*

# Keep these root files/folders tracked
!.gitignore
!README.md
!AGENTS.md
!firebase.json
!.firebaserc
!.github/
!.github/**

# Keep primary content folders tracked
!assignments/
!resources/
!students/
!teachers/

# Common OS/editor junk (ignored even inside whitelisted folders)
**/.DS_Store
**/Thumbs.db
**/*.log
**/~$*

